{"tid":2437522,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Jeff Bezos 前妻再婚 嫁給西雅圖自然科學老師","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T02:52:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f23a10858df76fd011f5ff3d93cac6b1c8603250","tid":2437522,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕億萬富翁慈善家斯科特（MacKenzie Scott）在2019年與亞馬遜創辦人貝佐斯（Jeff Bezos）離婚後，現傳出再婚消息，據悉斯科特的新丈夫名為朱伊特（Dan Jewett），為西雅圖1間私立學校的自然科學老師。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，朱伊特6日在由微軟公司創辦人比爾蓋茲（Bill Gates）夫婦和股神巴菲特（Warren Buffett）發起的「樂施誓約」（The Giving Pledge）網站上，宣布與斯科特的婚訊，稱他將與其所認識最慷慨、最善良的人之一結成連理，並將與斯科特一起致力於捐出巨額財富為他人服務。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3459484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3459484&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058iwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=53376473\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3459484&h=1ab7e259\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3459484</a>"},{"pid":"90e2c8a58ab3166f04f81b3529a7ed22f753e82b","tid":2437522,"uid":111019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"分身家師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afe369a695bcbcc118f79ece073a08dba27f0f1","tid":2437522,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90e2c8a58ab3166f04f81b3529a7ed22f753e82b","tid":2437522,"uid":111019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"分身家師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"現年50歲的麥肯齊去年和貝佐斯離婚後，分得亞馬遜（<a href=\"http://amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.com&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058iwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=72036f56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazon.com</a>）4%股份，當時價值350億美元（約1兆260億元台幣）。根據彭博億萬富豪指數（Bloomberg Billionaires Index），這位全球首富的前妻目前身家達600億美元（約1兆7595億元台幣）。"},{"pid":"bb040c9e4dc2d3e856d09b664aca19f5bfcfd36a","tid":2437522,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5afe369a695bcbcc118f79ece073a08dba27f0f1","tid":2437522,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90e2c8a58ab3166f04f81b3529a7ed22f753e82b","tid":2437522,"uid":111019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"分身家師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"現年50歲的麥肯齊去年和貝佐斯離婚後，分得亞馬遜（<a href=\"http://amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.com&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058iwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=72036f56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazon.com</a>）4%股份，當時價值350億美元（約1兆260億元台幣）。根據彭博億萬富豪指數（Bloomberg Billionaires Index），這位全球首富的前妻目前身家達600億美元（約1兆7595億元台幣）。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}